data.name: richTextBox3.Text
data.value:
Note: Call Baka MPlayer's name before you say the command, by default the name is "baka". You can change its name via the settings file (Baka MPlayer.settings)
open [file] mute unmute [increase/raise] volume volume up [decrease/lower] volume volume down hide show help stop listening close play pause rewind stop [next/skip] chapter previous chapter next [file] previous [file] [view/go] fullscreen [exit/leave] fullscreen whats playing
So for example, to pause the video you would say [baka pause].
